1
00:00:11,605 --> 00:00:16,008
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:16,076 --> 00:00:20,604
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:21,315 --> 00:00:25,445
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,519 --> 00:00:28,716
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,658 --> 00:00:32,922
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:32,993 --> 00:00:39,296
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:40,234 --> 00:00:44,671
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,738 --> 00:00:48,265
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:51,644
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,712 --> 00:00:54,647
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,715 --> 00:00:59,015
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:59,219 --> 00:01:01,483
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,555 --> 00:01:07,357
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,762 --> 00:01:11,098
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:11,098 --> 00:01:13,430
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:18,301
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,372 --> 00:01:20,567
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,641 --> 00:01:23,109
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:23,177 --> 00:01:26,544
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:44,375 --> 00:01:49,506
<i>The Secrets of the Mangekyo Sharingan</i>

21
00:02:16,074 --> 00:02:18,565
<i>No matter what darkness</i>
<i>might lie ahead,</i>

22
00:02:18,643 --> 00:02:20,508
<i>I will rush into it headfirst!</i>

23
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,608
<i>No matter what happens,</i>

24
00:02:23,681 --> 00:02:25,876
<i>I will get my hands</i>
<i>on that power!</i>

25
00:02:36,127 --> 00:02:38,061
<i>It's getting late...</i>

26
00:03:05,389 --> 00:03:06,686
<i>What was that?</i>

27
00:03:06,758 --> 00:03:08,988
<i>I thought I sensed</i>
<i>someone there just now...</i>

28
00:03:13,264 --> 00:03:14,561
<i>The lights...</i>

29
00:03:14,999 --> 00:03:17,490
<i>It isn't even close</i>
<i>to bedtime yet...</i>

30
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:23,365
This is...!

31
00:03:27,812 --> 00:03:29,803
Wh-What <i>is</i> this...?!

32
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:35,045
<i>What the hell is this?!</i>

33
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:41,187
Uncle... Aunt...

34
00:03:45,663 --> 00:03:47,824
Father... Mother...

35
00:03:56,073 --> 00:03:58,064
Father? Mother?

36
00:04:28,973 --> 00:04:30,201
<i>There's somebody in there!</i>

37
00:04:38,883 --> 00:04:40,043
<i>Move!</i>

38
00:04:41,219 --> 00:04:42,049
<i>Move!</i>

39
00:04:43,521 --> 00:04:44,545
<i>Move!</i>

40
00:04:50,094 --> 00:04:51,584
Father! Mother!

41
00:05:18,289 --> 00:05:19,620
Big Brother!

42
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:22,420
Big Brother!
Father and Mother are...!

43
00:05:22,793 --> 00:05:24,920
Why? For what reason?!

44
00:05:25,897 --> 00:05:27,421
Who the hell would do
something like this...?!

45
00:05:33,638 --> 00:05:35,629
Big Brother... what are?

46
00:05:43,414 --> 00:05:46,076
What are you doing, Big Brother?!

47
00:05:47,018 --> 00:05:49,714
You pathetic younger brother...

48
00:05:57,261 --> 00:05:58,888
Mangekyo Sharingan!

49
00:06:08,773 --> 00:06:11,970
Stop! Big Brother!

50
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:15,143
Don't make me see
this kind of thing!

51
00:06:16,647 --> 00:06:17,773
Why...?!

52
00:06:18,716 --> 00:06:20,513
Big Brother, why did you?!

53
00:06:48,412 --> 00:06:49,902
Why...

54
00:06:51,682 --> 00:06:54,879
Big Brother... Why did you?

55
00:06:57,788 --> 00:07:01,656
In order to measure my vessel...

56
00:07:02,593 --> 00:07:05,562
To measure your vessel?

57
00:07:07,465 --> 00:07:08,693
Is that all?

58
00:07:12,636 --> 00:07:16,766
Only for that reason...
you killed everybody...?

59
00:07:20,277 --> 00:07:22,108
That is what is important.

60
00:07:23,681 --> 00:07:25,444
What the hell is that?

61
00:07:28,552 --> 00:07:31,146
You gotta be kidding!

62
00:07:53,411 --> 00:07:54,537
<i>I'm scared...</i>

63
00:07:55,312 --> 00:07:56,472
<i>I'm scared!</i>

64
00:08:11,462 --> 00:08:14,727
Don't kill me...!

65
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,954
I don't believe it!

66
00:08:44,028 --> 00:08:47,327
This is too unlike you, Big Brother.
I mean...

67
00:08:47,398 --> 00:08:50,799
The reason I acted as the big brother
you desired was...

68
00:08:51,435 --> 00:08:54,529
because I wanted to
measure your vessel.

69
00:08:55,906 --> 00:09:00,741
You have the potential
to become my opponent

70
00:09:00,811 --> 00:09:03,780
in order for me to measure
my vessel.

71
00:09:05,316 --> 00:09:09,218
You hated me...

72
00:09:10,054 --> 00:09:13,148
and you continued to have
the desire to surpass me.

73
00:09:14,258 --> 00:09:16,419
That's exactly why
I will allow you to live...

74
00:09:17,128 --> 00:09:19,187
for my own benefit.

75
00:09:19,263 --> 00:09:24,394
You are someone who could be able to use
Mangekyo Sharingan just like me.

76
00:09:27,171 --> 00:09:30,140
However, on one condition...

77
00:09:34,545 --> 00:09:39,881
That you must kill
your closest friend...

78
00:09:42,786 --> 00:09:44,310
Y-You've gotta be kidding...

79
00:09:48,592 --> 00:09:52,119
Just like I did...

80
00:09:54,064 --> 00:09:56,999
<i>Regarding Shisui Uchiha</i>
<i>who committed suicide last night</i>

81
00:09:57,067 --> 00:09:59,763
<i>by throwing himself into</i>
<i>the Nakano River...</i>

82
00:10:01,672 --> 00:10:05,608
<i>The other one that did not show up</i>
<i>to the meeting is Shisui...</i>

83
00:10:05,676 --> 00:10:08,144
<i>If I remember correctly...</i>

84
00:10:08,212 --> 00:10:10,772
<i>you adored him like</i>
<i>he was your real older brother...</i>

85
00:10:11,749 --> 00:10:14,650
That was... your doing...?

86
00:10:16,187 --> 00:10:18,883
Big Brother, you... killed Shisui?!

87
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:23,617
That's right... and because of
that I obtained these eyes.

88
00:10:25,996 --> 00:10:28,362
The main hall of Nakano Shrine...

89
00:10:28,432 --> 00:10:31,993
Underneath the seventh tatami mat
on the far right

90
00:10:32,069 --> 00:10:34,537
is the secret gathering place
of the Clan.

91
00:10:36,373 --> 00:10:39,900
There you will find recorded
the secret of...

92
00:10:39,977 --> 00:10:46,746
the raison d'être of
the Uchiha Clan's Visual Jutsu.

93
00:10:48,052 --> 00:10:50,384
<i>The secret of the raison d'étre...?</i>

94
00:10:52,022 --> 00:10:54,320
If you attain these eyes,

95
00:10:54,391 --> 00:10:57,189
you will become the third person
including myself

96
00:10:57,261 --> 00:11:00,492
to utilize
the Mangekyo Sharingan.

97
00:11:01,465 --> 00:11:02,932
If that happens...

98
00:11:04,435 --> 00:11:07,336
then there will have been meaning
in my allowing you to live.

99
00:11:07,871 --> 00:11:10,135
However... at present...

100
00:11:11,942 --> 00:11:14,536
You are not worth killing.

101
00:11:15,479 --> 00:11:17,447
My pathetic younger brother...

102
00:11:17,514 --> 00:11:20,347
If you want to kill me,
then begrudge me!

103
00:11:20,551 --> 00:11:21,813
Hate me!

104
00:11:22,219 --> 00:11:25,552
And live in an ugly manner...

105
00:11:25,923 --> 00:11:30,155
Run away... run away...
and cling to life...

106
00:11:30,694 --> 00:11:34,630
And one day, when you have
the same eyes as I do...

107
00:11:35,332 --> 00:11:37,027
come and stand before me!

108
00:11:57,621 --> 00:11:58,781
<i>A dream...?</i>

109
00:12:14,538 --> 00:12:16,665
Yes... that's right.

110
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:19,641
The only one who survived...
is that boy.

111
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:23,204
Didn't he have
an older brother?

112
00:12:24,882 --> 00:12:28,010
Yes, but he's gone missing...

113
00:12:30,721 --> 00:12:34,885
It can't be true...
That elite Uchiha Clan...

114
00:13:03,253 --> 00:13:07,212
Hi, Sasuke! What did you
come to buy today?

115
00:13:43,527 --> 00:13:46,155
<i>Sasuke, are you on your way to school?</i>

116
00:13:46,263 --> 00:13:47,287
<i>Yeah.</i>

117
00:13:50,401 --> 00:13:53,837
<i>I saw Itachi earlier,</i>
<i>but he's very admirable, isn't he?</i>

118
00:13:54,104 --> 00:13:56,299
<i>He's already become</i>
<i>a top class Shinobi.</i>

119
00:13:56,940 --> 00:14:00,034
<i>He graduated from the Ninja Academy</i>
<i>at the top of his class at age seven</i>

120
00:14:00,110 --> 00:14:03,136
<i>and attained the rank</i>
<i>of Chunin at age ten, didn't he?</i>

121
00:14:03,781 --> 00:14:06,341
<i>He was able to use Sharingan</i>
<i>when he was eight!</i>

122
00:14:08,452 --> 00:14:10,317
<i>That's true, isn't it?</i>

123
00:14:10,387 --> 00:14:14,687
<i>That boy is truly the pride</i>
<i>of the Uchiha Clan.</i>

124
00:14:52,930 --> 00:14:55,364
<i>Welcome home...Sasuke!</i>

125
00:15:26,396 --> 00:15:27,556
<i>Sasuke...!</i>

126
00:15:28,265 --> 00:15:29,254
<i>Wait a second...</i>

127
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,294
<i>What is it?</i>

128
00:15:42,045 --> 00:15:43,103
Mother?!

129
00:15:55,926 --> 00:15:57,951
<i>Then why only Big Brother!</i>

130
00:16:01,365 --> 00:16:04,493
<i>Your brother's your brother.</i>
<i>And you are you.</i>

131
00:16:04,568 --> 00:16:07,935
<i>Father cares deeply</i>
<i>about both of you.</i>

132
00:16:57,621 --> 00:17:00,249
<i>The main hall of Nakano Shrine...</i>

133
00:17:02,125 --> 00:17:05,253
<i>Located underneath</i>
<i>the seventh tatami mat on the far right</i>

134
00:17:05,329 --> 00:17:08,059
<i>is our clan's secret gathering place...</i>

135
00:17:14,705 --> 00:17:18,573
I see... So that's what it is...

136
00:17:20,711 --> 00:17:23,874
Ninja Academy

137
00:17:24,481 --> 00:17:26,449
Hey, Shikamaru...

138
00:17:26,516 --> 00:17:28,541
Wanna go to the candy shop
after school?

139
00:17:28,619 --> 00:17:30,086
Huh... No way.

140
00:17:30,354 --> 00:17:33,619
You can do that 'cuz
your mother's nice,

141
00:17:33,690 --> 00:17:37,148
but if my mother found out that I bought
myself a snack before going home,

142
00:17:37,227 --> 00:17:39,718
I'd be in big trouble.

143
00:17:40,263 --> 00:17:41,628
Did you hear the news...

144
00:17:41,698 --> 00:17:44,758
that entire Uchiha Clan
was apparently murdered?

145
00:17:44,935 --> 00:17:47,870
Yeah, my dad told me.

146
00:17:48,472 --> 00:17:51,441
Apparently he's the only one
who survived...

147
00:18:07,224 --> 00:18:09,818
<i>That's my boy.</i>

148
00:18:10,994 --> 00:18:14,521
<i>With me, you're all</i>
<i>your father talks about...</i>

149
00:18:21,271 --> 00:18:26,573
I wonder... what kind of things
Father was saying to Mother...

150
00:18:37,788 --> 00:18:39,915
<i>If you want to kill me...</i>

151
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:42,185
<i>Begrudge me! Hate me!</i>

152
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:51,631
<i>If it's for the purpose of killing you,</i>

153
00:18:51,702 --> 00:18:55,502
<i>I will rush headfirst into whatever</i>
<i>darkness which may lie ahead!</i>

154
00:18:56,373 --> 00:18:59,774
<i>I will obtain that power no matter what!</i>

155
00:19:00,544 --> 00:19:03,411
<i>From this point onwards,</i>
<i>I am an avenger!</i>

156
00:19:06,349 --> 00:19:09,876
<i>Sasuke is now</i>
<i>in depths of darkness...</i>

157
00:19:10,887 --> 00:19:12,787
<i>If you stop in a place like this...</i>

158
00:19:12,856 --> 00:19:15,290
<i>you won't be able to catch up</i>
<i>with Sasuke.</i>

159
00:19:36,046 --> 00:19:38,844
<i>Neji, it's just like you said.</i>

160
00:19:39,549 --> 00:19:41,949
<i>That guy looks like he's in</i>
<i>the depths of darkness right now...</i>

161
00:19:43,954 --> 00:19:47,788
<i>He really hit me with</i>
<i>his full strength! Damn it!</i>

162
00:19:52,662 --> 00:19:58,532
Don't you consider me...
your comrade any longer?!

163
00:19:59,703 --> 00:20:05,164
Don't all those things we did together
in Squad Seven mean anything to you?!

164
00:20:07,811 --> 00:20:08,573
No.

165
00:20:10,247 --> 00:20:14,149
<i>I will get my hands on</i>
<i>that power no matter what.</i>

166
00:20:15,519 --> 00:20:17,419
It wasn't meaningless...

167
00:20:17,687 --> 00:20:23,853
To me, you became my...
closest friend.

168
00:20:25,495 --> 00:20:27,929
We've become... friends?

169
00:20:28,999 --> 00:20:30,398
Then... why?!

170
00:20:30,467 --> 00:20:32,264
All the more reason why...

171
00:20:33,637 --> 00:20:35,332
All the more reason why...

172
00:20:35,405 --> 00:20:38,806
there's meaning in taking
you down.

173
00:20:44,314 --> 00:20:46,612
I don't fully understand but...

174
00:20:47,184 --> 00:20:51,018
I understood that you want to
fight me with your everything!

175
00:20:51,621 --> 00:20:52,986
Sasuke...!

176
00:21:12,375 --> 00:21:17,039
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

177
00:21:17,113 --> 00:21:23,416
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

178
00:21:23,486 --> 00:21:33,987
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

179
00:21:34,297 --> 00:21:43,763
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

180
00:21:45,508 --> 00:21:50,502
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

181
00:21:50,814 --> 00:21:59,813
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

182
00:22:01,992 --> 00:22:11,526
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

183
00:22:12,969 --> 00:22:21,968
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

184
00:22:30,854 --> 00:22:34,722
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

185
00:22:38,962 --> 00:22:42,989
Are you trying to take me
down for real?

186
00:22:44,034 --> 00:22:45,797
I don't know any longer

187
00:22:45,869 --> 00:22:48,667
whether you really meant
what you said earlier or not!

188
00:22:48,939 --> 00:22:53,433
Could it be that it was only I
who thought we were friends?

189
00:22:54,244 --> 00:22:58,977
If that's the case,
I'm just a really lame guy...

190
00:22:59,049 --> 00:23:00,983
Aren't I? Sasuke?

191
00:23:01,418 --> 00:23:03,682
Nex. T episode: " For a Friend
